{"tid":2371537,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：看不到公務員宣誓或簽署聲明會影響同事士氣","createTime":"2021-01-19T03:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T12:12:07.000Z","uid":283021,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6dba60d74c6fcf533e7c3ce68d6672ae060432e5","tid":2371537,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"政府要求現職公務員在4星期內簽署聲明，擁護基本法和效忠特區。行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，要求公務員宣誓是入職時應有的理念，公務員入職當然要支持特區及特區政府，支持基本法落實一國兩制，因此宣誓及簽署聲明是理所當然，展示出公務員明白公眾對他們有期望。有關安排去年7月先適用於新入職公務員，4000多位新入職公務員都樂意簽署。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又表示，看不到宣誓或簽署聲明的要求會影響同事士氣，亦看不到這與公務員士氣有直接關係，如果部分公務員或工會對此有意見，相信公務員事務局局長樂意進行溝通。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571157-20210119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571157-20210119.htm&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrM%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=981a20a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571157-20210119.htm&h=7f94ae62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571157-20210119.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n又睇唔到 ！"},{"pid":"40017dd05d144d3d36897c29c8804babee9a7318","tid":2371537,"uid":226466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"林鄭（視覺缺陷）"},{"pid":"96dfb9ae7d91bfdfbe2ca207697de30e646869df","tid":2371537,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"用開邊隻眼睇野？"},{"pid":"31a44f21542d7bf17b069d3b94c1562afe520074","tid":2371537,"uid":31962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"公務員士氣同放屁一樣當然睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0671835424d9fd43e507bb14d4e94e398f2153db","tid":2371537,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:08:19.000Z","msg":"是撚旦啦"},{"pid":"69ce0c64fb53e310b8a046fe7bdd01a3bd20146c","tid":2